name: {DD} Reverse cowgirl anal frames
description:
Reverse cowgirl anal Lora. Also it can create a template for gifs.

I am not that happy with the result, but it works.

Tags

1girl - +lower weight, for one girl reverse cowgirl anal

4girls - for 4 fames with the same girl

I haven't prepared pictures for real sex, for now it's only dildos. I'll retrain it later with more pictures.

Tends to create disgusting feet, so put it (feet) to the negative prompt, or inpaint it later.

I recomend try it on 512x512 and then upscale using imgToimg.

768x768 and 1024x1024 tends to create weird sets of images, but you may find it interesting, so feel free to experiement.

Versions

v1

Trained on perfectDeliberate, photorealistic, more flexible with 1girl tag

v2

Trained on anythingv4.5, photorealistic, less flexible, but give more consistency

v3

Retrained on bigger dataset and better quality pictures. For frames picture use square canvas and 4girls, 2x2frames tags.

Use 1girl and don't use 2x2frames if you want to get one image of dildo riding.

v3r

Basically it's a different model, which is trained on sex pictures only. So no toys here. Works in the best way with my dpgd model, but usable with any other. May not work with anime models though. These one use 3x3frames (768x768) and 1frame (any resolution) tags.

My guide is still usable.

Enjoy)

Feel free to ask any questions here in comments, or in my discord channel.

Also I am making games with AI arts. They will be free in the future, but if you want to participate in making or have an early access - you can support me on patreon)

Also my wet hair Lora was banned here, I dunno why. You can download the last version of it from my patreon for free.
